Package: mstut
Title: A tutorial to learn basics of mass spectrometry in R.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Laurent", "Gatto",
                  email = "lg390@cam.ac.uk",
	   	  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a simple tutorial describing the basics
	     of mass spectrometry. It provides functions that can be
	     used to plots and generate simple animations describing
	     mass spectrometry and a vignette as the main tutorial.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
URL: https://github.com/lgatto/mstut
BugReports: https://github.com/lgatto/mstut/issues
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, BiocStyle, animation
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
